==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[metal]] [[detector]]}}
# A [[hand-held]] [[device]] that uses [[electromagnetic induction]] to [[detect]] [[buried]] metal.
# A [[structure]], similar to a [[doorway]], through which people [[pass]]; an [[alarm]] is [[sounded]] if the person is carrying a metal object.

